race.comment: Fancy the returning HOT DIGITY BOOM (2) finds the right race to return a winner. He shaped with real promise from the get-go and earned himself a couple of shots in better races last prep. Held up well in a couple those and he has jumped out nearly for this return. MERCURIAL LADY (14) was outdashed at Pakenham last time but she is a better horse when the pace is stronger and she should get that here. She has been a bit frustrating at times but the talent is there. STORMBOURG (20) brings a nice profile to the table, second up off a nice return which is the same spot that we find MARKDEL (9) who was able to win after nine months off the scene and was also able to score second up last prep which bodes well.
